$ SAY "ROMIT -- ROM LATEST STARWARS SYSTEM "$ SW$ SAY "CLEAR OUT STARWARS DIRECTORY"$ DEL *.CMN;*,*.EQU;*,*.ERR.*,*.LNK;*,*.LIS;*,*.MAC;*,*.OBJ;*/NOCONFIRM$ DEL LINKIT.COM;*/NOCONFIRM$ DIR$ SAY "COPY WS FILES INTO STARWARS"$ WS$ !	COPY *.CMN SW:$ !	COPY *.EQU SW:$ COPY [.OBJ]*.OBJ SW:$ COPY *.LNK SW:$ !	COPY HLL69F.MAC SW:$ !	COPY MOP69.MAC SW:$ !	COPY VG*.MAC SW:$ !	COPY WSCOMN.MAC SW:$ COPY LINKIT.COM SW:$ !$ !	COPY TCEROM.MAC SW:$ !	COPY TCTEST.MAC SW:$ !	COPY WSINT.MAC SW:$ SW$ DIR$ !$ !	SAY "EDIT PROGRAMS, CHANGE DEVSYS==1 TO DEVSYS==0"$ !	SAY "SEARCH FOR DEVSYS, CHANGE 1 TO 0, EXIT"$ !	EDEV :== EDIT/EDT/COMMAND=ROMIT.EDT$ !	EDEV TCEROM.MAC$ !	EDEV TCTEST.MAC$ !	EDEV WSINT.MAC$ !$ !	SAY "FINISHED CONVERTING SOURCE TO ROM, NOW MAC THEM"$ !	MAC69 TCEROM$ !	MAC69 TCTEST$ !	MAC69 WSINT$ !$ !	DIR/DATE *.ERR$ !	SAY "ALL DONE WITH MAC'ING, TRY LINKING"$ LINKIT$ !$ SAY "LINK ALL DONE"$ SAY "CHECK FOR MAC ERRORS, CHECK FOR LINK ERRORS"$ !$ EXIT